      "type": "LinguisticObject",
      "content": "The public Sotheby's Photographs auction (sale N08533), New York, 2009, carried out by Sotheby's, at which Sun & Rain Works consigned an Ansel Adams photograph, 'San Francisco from Twin Peaks' (lot 16). Sun & Rain Works designates its engagement with this auction as the material of the conceptual work The Auction as Artwork. This record names the real-world event and cites the public catalogue; it does not assert that Sotheby's authored, endorsed, or participated in the artwork, and the catalogue does not name Sun & Rain Works.",
